<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-77-0782 </DOCNO><TEXT>Various papers on gas laser technology are presented. The general topicsaddressed include: industrial excimer lasers, excimer laser physics andtechnology, novel applications of excimer lasers in medicine and communications,visible and infrared gas laser technology. Individual subjects discussedinclude: imaging excimer laser radars, rapid tuning mechanism for CO{sub2} lasers, ultrastable CO{sub 2} lasers, design of a CO{sub 2} laserfor second harmonic generation, design of a (C-13)(O-16)2 laser amplifier,performance of high power copper vapor lasers in an injection-controlledoscillator-amplifier configuration.</TEXT></DOC>